title: E113 ERIK GRIFFIN THE COMEDIAN - IMPAULSIVE EP. 113

description:
Actor and stand-up comedian Erik Griffin speaks on the art of texting to woo the opposite sex, getting exposed in the DMs, the sensitive state of comedy in the entertainment industry, Jake Paul’s tumultuous relationships, and the asteroid that’s going to kill us all.
